name: Imnotamember.GitHub.io
body:
![Dr. Boxhead](http://github.com/imnotamember/imnotamember.github.io/tree/master/images/drBoxhead.png) This is a place for me to store and document my progress through the wonderful world of programming and scientific research. It also will supply information on my work as a graduate student in the PhD program at the University of Nebraska -- Lincoln. I am in the Psychology-Neuroscience and Behavior program. If you have questions/ideas/collaborations, feel free to email me at joshua.e.zosky@gmail.com.

Current Project:

Programming-Workshop

FaceReader bindings for Python
